title: NIN QOTSA 2013 Live Collection
description:
In anticipation of the upcoming the awesome but sadly only in AUS/NZ,  Nine Inch Nails + Queens of the Stone Age tour, I have compiled this amazing live collection featuring official releases, soundboard audio, and fan taped recordings. It includes the following;


NIN
- Nine Inch Nails Live EP 2013
- A soundboard compilation from the summer festival circuit.
- A crowdsourced compilation of every song played during the Tension 2013 fall arena tour.

QOTSA
- Itunes Festival EP
- Like Cologne EP
- A soundboard compilation from the Like Clockwork tour. 


Thank you to the rippers, tapers, and websites like reflecting in the chrome or heavy soundboard bloggers! Please support the bands, buy the ticket, take the ride.
